ActAeronautics Act
SubjectInterim Order No. 5 Respecting Flight Deck Occupants
PrecisOrder approving INTERIM ORDER NO. 5 RESPECTING FLIGHT DECK OCCUPANTS, made by the Minister of Transport on June 16, 2016, in order to prevent a lone flight crew member with malicious intent from purposely denying entry on the flight to the second flight crew member or other authorized personnel.
